The FCDO advises against all but essential travel to:
the whole of Guadeloupe based on the current assessment of COVID-19 risks.
If you are returning to the UK from Guadeloupe, you will need to self-isolate on your return (unless you are exempt). Check the latest guidance for England, Northern Ireland, Scotland and Wales.
